---
import ArticleLayout from '../../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<ArticleLayout
  title="The Abolition of Man Study Guide"
  author="Gregory the Great Institute"
  date="December 2025"
  category="Resource"
  image="/images/art/gozzoli-triumph-aquinas.jpg"
  imageAlt="Triumph of St Thomas Aquinas by Benozzo Gozzoli"
  related={[
    { title: "2026 Book Studies — Inklings Clubs", href: `${base}programs/book-studies/`, meta: "Program · Join a group" },
    { title: "5 Ways to Celebrate Easter as a Family", href: `${base}library/easter-family/`, meta: "Resource · Catherine Renneberg" },
  ]}
>
  <p>
    C.S. Lewis's <em>The Abolition of Man</em> is one of the most important works of the
    twentieth century — a short, devastating critique of moral relativism and a defence of
    natural law that remains as urgent today as when it was written in 1943.
  </p>

  <p>
    This study guide is designed for use in reading groups, classrooms, and individual study.
    It provides chapter-by-chapter discussion questions, key passages for reflection, and
    background context to help readers engage more deeply with Lewis's argument.
  </p>

  <p>
    Whether you're leading an Inklings Club, teaching a class, or simply reading on your own,
    this guide will help you get more out of one of the great books of the Western tradition.
  </p>

  <h2>What's Included</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Chapter-by-chapter discussion questions</li>
    <li>Key passages highlighted for close reading</li>
    <li>Historical and philosophical context</li>
    <li>Suggestions for further reading</li>
    <li>Leader's notes for group facilitators</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="resource-download">
    <h3 class="resource-download__heading">Get this study guide</h3>
    <p class="resource-download__desc">Enter your email and we'll send you a copy.</p>
    <form class="resource-download__form" data-ac-endpoint="/api/subscribe" data-ac-success="Check your inbox for the download link!" method="POST">
      <input type="hidden" name="resource" value="abolition-of-man-guide" />
      <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="Email address" aria-label="Email address" />
      <button type="submit">Email Me a Copy</button>
    </form>
    <label class="resource-download__optin">
      <input type="checkbox" name="magnalia_letter" value="yes" />
      <span>I'd like to receive future resources and essays from <strong>Magnalia Letter</strong></span>
    </label>
  </div>
</ArticleLayout>

<style>
  .resource-download {
    background: var(--color-linen);
    border: 1px solid rgba(198, 160, 50, 0.3);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 28px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .resource-download__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .resource-download__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body) !important;
    font-size: 0.88rem !important;
    color: var(--color-gray) !important;
    margin-bottom: 16px !important;
  }

  .resource-download__form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .resource-download__form :global(input[type="email"]) {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.2);
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    min-width: 200px;
    outline: none;
  }

  .resource-download__form :global(input[type="email"]):focus {
    border-color: var(--color-gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(198, 160, 50, 0.15);
  }

  .resource-download__form :global(button) {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: var(--color-crimson);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .resource-download__form :global(button:hover) {
    background: #6b1d00;
  }

  .resource-download__optin {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .resource-download__optin :global(input[type="checkbox"]) {
    margin-top: 2px;
    accent-color: var(--color-gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .resource-download__optin :global(strong) {
    color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  .article__body :global(ul) {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .article__body :global(li) {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
</style>
